---
title: Silver Knight Archer Skip (SKAS)
hidden: false
---
**Silver Knight Archer Skip** also known as SKAS is a skip that **allows** you to reach [Ornstein](http://darksouls.wikidot.com/dragon-slayer-ornstein-executioner-smough) & [Smough ](http://darksouls.wikidot.com/dragon-slayer-ornstein-executioner-smough)without having to deal with the **Silver Knight archers**. It also **allows** you to get to the [Giant **Blacksmith**](http://darksouls.wikidot.com/giant-blacksmith) very quickly and reach **O&S** faster than usual.

This glitch uses [Memeroll](/ds1remaster/fall-damages-cancel#air-rolls) combined with Fall control for the standard method and [fall control plunge damage cancel](/ds1remaster/fall-damages-cancel#fall-control-plunge-damage-cancel) for the alternative method.

> There is no reason to use alternative SKAS anymore because it is slower.

[This skip was discovered on december 2017 on PTDE version of the game by **Kahmul**](https://youtu.be/g_1K2hLDb3c).

## Resources

- Standard SKAS : [https://youtu.be/gKEObUDsGT8](https://youtu.be/gKEObUDsGT8) by San on YouTube.
- Alternative SKAS: [https://youtu.be/ygNCa4UL634](https://youtu.be/ygNCa4UL634) by San on Youtube.
